content: New texter. I'd like to share with my social media networks that I am doing texting. Is there a share button somewhere? Or what is the best landing page to send people to? Just want to make sure I am giving folks the most direct links so that they can potentially volunteer. thanks.
Hi <@1292256585908883476> - Thanks for volunteering. The best link to share about volunteering in general is  our webpage:  https://go.kamalaharris.com/?utm_source=hfp_w_kh_menu.
